<item>
            <title>[LU-14469] lmv_rmfid() does 128K kmalloc()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14469</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When &lt;tt&gt;ll_rmfid()&lt;/tt&gt; is called with 4096 FIDs (which is the max) then &lt;tt&gt;lmv_rmfid()&lt;/tt&gt; will kmalloc() a 128K &lt;tt&gt;fid_array&lt;/tt&gt;. Seen running sanity 421d locally:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
